overview: WCW's annual Fall extravaganza hosts one of the biggest matches of all time when Sting takes on Hulk Hogan for the WCW World Heavyweight Championship. Goldberg battles "Diamond" Dallas Page. The West Texas Rednecks defend the WCW World Tag Team Championship against Harlem Heat. Plus, Rey Misterio Jr., Eddy Guerrero, and more!
title: WCW Fall Brawl 1999
